Background*
Mr. Zan Shengda, also known as Louis, serves as the President of Jiangsu Zongyi Co. Ltd and has been General Manager since June 29, 2016. Mr. Shengda has been the Chairman of the Board at Jiangsu Zongyi Co. Ltd since June 29, 2016. Mr. Shengda served as the Chairman and General Manager of Jiangsu Zongyi Co. Ltd. and serves as its Director.









