Interests, Passion, Hobbies

Kind of Interests, Passion and Hobbies: Family
Description: Enjoys spending time with family, including shopping with wife, and playing chess and sports with daughter.


Kind of Interests, Passion and Hobbies: Politics
Description: Member of Communist Party of China (CPC). Serves as a Representative of the 12th National People's Congress (NPC).


Kind of Interests, Passion and Hobbies: Finance - Investment
Description: Invested in China International Futures, the largest futures company in China.

Contact us to see more Interests, Passion, Hobbies
Philanthropy

Giving Profile: Majority of philanthropic activities appears to be through Zongyi Group, of which Zan is Chairman and majority Shareholder. The Group donates primarily to educational and social causes. Notable donations include $1.5 million to establish the "Zongyi Talent Education Fund" in 2003; $150,000 to establish the "Hope Elementary School" following the Sichuan earthquake, and $3 million to the Nantong Tongzhou Charitable Foundation in 2008; and an undisclosed amount towards the construction of the Shengda Building at Nanjing University in 2012. Zan also serves as Vice Chairman and Executive Director of Nantong Tongzhou Charitable Foundation, and Honorary Director at Nanjing University. He does not appear to have a family foundation.

